# Cloudflare Workers AI Configuration (OPTIONAL - Free Tier Available)
# Get these from: https://dash.cloudflare.com/
# Navigate to: AI > Workers AI > Get API Token

CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=your_account_id_here
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=your_api_token_here

# How to get these:
# 1. Sign up for Cloudflare (free): https://dash.cloudflare.com/sign-up
# 2. Go to Workers & Pages > AI
# 3. Click "Get Started" or "Use AI"
# 4. Your Account ID is visible in the URL: /accounts/<THIS_IS_YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID>/
# 5. Create an API Token:
#    - Go to My Profile > API Tokens
#    - Click "Create Token"
#    - Use "Edit Cloudflare Workers" template
#    - Or create custom token with "Workers AI" permissions
# 6. Copy your Account ID and API Token to .env.local

# Free Tier Limits (as of 2024):
# - 10,000 neurons (requests) per day
# - No credit card required
# - Access to Llama 3.1 8B Instruct and other models

# Note: If these are not set, the app falls back to pattern matching only (still works!)
